<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
    integrity="sha384-KK94CHFLLe+nY2dmCWGMq91rCGa5gtU4mk92HdvYe+M/SXH301p5ILy+dN9+nJOZ" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/homepage.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include("header.ejs") %>
    <div class="container px-4 py-5">
    
        <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 align-items-md-center g-5 py-5">
          <div class="col d-flex flex-column align-items-start gap-2">
            <h2 class="fw-bold text-body-emphasis">Financial calculators for all your personal needs is right here.</h2>
            <p class="text-body-secondary"></p>
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Check yourself</a>
          </div>
    
          <div class="col">
            <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-sm-2 g-4">
              <div class="col d-flex flex-column gap-2">
                <div class="feature-icon-small d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center text-bg-primary bg-gradient fs-4 rounded-3">
                  <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em">
                    <use xlink:href="#collection"></use>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h4 class="fw-semibold mb-0 text-body-emphasis">Comprehensive Calculator Selection</h4>
                <p class="text-body-secondary">Provide a wide range of financial calculators covering various aspects such as investment planning, loan calculations, retirement planning, tax calculations, and more. Ensure the calculators cater to different financial needs and goals of users.</p>
              </div>
    
              <div class="col d-flex flex-column gap-2">
                <div class="feature-icon-small d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center text-bg-primary bg-gradient fs-4 rounded-3">
                  <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em">
                    <use xlink:href="#gear-fill"></use>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h4 class="fw-semibold mb-0 text-body-emphasis">Customization Options</h4>
                <p class="text-body-secondary"> Offer customization features allowing users to input their specific financial details such as investment amount, interest rate, tenure, etc. This customization enhances the accuracy of the calculations and provides tailored results based on individual financial scenarios.</p>
              </div>
    
              <div class="col d-flex flex-column gap-2">
                <div class="feature-icon-small d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center text-bg-primary bg-gradient fs-4 rounded-3">
                  <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em">
                    <use xlink:href="#speedometer"></use>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h4 class="fw-semibold mb-0 text-body-emphasis">Interactive Graphs and Charts</h4>
                <p class="text-body-secondary">Integrate visual representations like graphs and charts to illustrate the calculated results. Visualizations help users better understand the financial implications of their decisions and enable them to analyze data intuitively.</p>
              </div>
    
              <div class="col d-flex flex-column gap-2">
                <div class="feature-icon-small d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center text-bg-primary bg-gradient fs-4 rounded-3">
                  <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em">
                    <use xlink:href="#table"></use>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h4 class="fw-semibold mb-0 text-body-emphasis">Educational Resources</h4>
                <p class="text-body-secondary">Provide educational resources such as articles, guides, and FAQs related to financial planning, investment strategies, and understanding financial terms. These resources complement the calculators, helping users make informed financial decisions and improve their financial literacy.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <%- include("footer.ejs") %>
      <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>